{"tid":2430722,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《新倚天屠龍記》王晶親證另有映期　公開Janice Man最新高清海報","createTime":"2021-03-03T06:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T13:24:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"acc1c5764babacb487ee92e7713c1f4ef8160519","tid":2430722,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T06:32:45.000Z","msg":"王晶去年宣布開拍《新倚天屠龍記》，引起影迷瘋狂熱議及期待。上星期耳東影業公布了2021的片單及檔期，當中就連《新倚天屠龍記》都有上映期，正當大家高興終於有個日子可以期待一下時，王晶在微博又有最新消息！<br />\n<br />\n日前耳東影業宣布《新倚天屠龍記》會在9月上映，不過28日王晶在微博寫下︰「特此聲明，《新倚天屠龍記》與耳東影業已解除合作協議。一切發行、宣傳、權益，與耳東影業並無關係。上映日期亦未確定，並非網上流傳之九月。而耳東影業目前並未持有任何《新倚天屠龍記》之股份。主控公司為香港星王朝。敬請垂注。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，王晶更公開了兩張Janice Man文詠珊飾演趙敏、徐錦江飾演謝遜（金毛獅王）的高清海報，不少影迷都留言指出「最期待文詠珊，感覺和趙敏氣質很搭配」、「文詠珊真的太美啦」、「謝遜還是那個謝遜」、「王導什麼時候上映？迫不及待了」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210303/443765095957532672653718.jpeg/zW6kHiOLWt6rq5DN8OrR1MxTaVINhWi0kTYSZpE2EmY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210303%2F443765095957532672653718.jpeg%2FzW6kHiOLWt6rq5DN8OrR1MxTaVINhWi0kTYSZpE2EmY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1d6e0a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210303/443765093361127424643715.jpeg/fxZoFyaw2HsxMQDaamihil--lO2PZRYGQe_bsEHv27A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210303%2F443765093361127424643715.jpeg%2FfxZoFyaw2HsxMQDaamihil--lO2PZRYGQe_bsEHv27A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a1964ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210303/443765090500481024481236.jpeg/KR3isZxI0HACtVze4yVKcLQ57rOjZ--WBkW_IQZFvyE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210303%2F443765090500481024481236.jpeg%2FKR3isZxI0HACtVze4yVKcLQ57rOjZ--WBkW_IQZFvyE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=4af545cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210303/44376